Job Duties & Responsibilities:

Mainly responsible for AR related functions;
Perform daily accounting operations and assist in credit control;
Provide clerical support to the team including data entry and document filing;
Perform other ad hoc duties as assigned.

Requirements:

LCCI higher or above;
At least 5 years commercial experience with 2 years in AR function is highly preferred;
Mature, good numeric sense, detail-minded and able to work independently;
Good communication and interpersonal skills;
Proficient in MS Office such as Outlook, Excel and Word;
Familiar with Flex System is an advantage;
Immediate available is highly preferred.
Attractive package commensurate with experience and qualification will be given to the successful candidate. Our staff members' performance and contribution will be recognized and fairly rewarded.  Please apply with full resume, date of available, current & expected salary toHuman Resources Manager, Toyo Mall Limited, 6/F, V Heun Building, 138 Queen’s Road Central, Hong Kong.  Applicants who wish to learn more about our Company may email the Human Resources Manager for more information.  Those who do not hear from us within 4 weeks may consider their applications not successful in this instance.

